4.1. If Source Code lawfully obtained under this License becomes subject to a License Change Notice, each recipient who lawfully possessed such Source Code before the effective date of the License Change Notice may continue to compile and build Binaries from that Source Code during the Transition Period only.

4.2. Any Binary validly built during the Transition Period shall be deemed a Binary validly built under this License and shall retain the redistribution rights stated in Section 5.

4.3. Upon expiration of the Transition Period, no person may further compile, build, rebuild, package, or otherwise create new Binaries from the affected Source Code unless permitted under the replacement license or under separate written permission from the Licensor.

