5.2. The rights granted in Section 5.1 survive any later License Change Notice, any later relicensing of the Source Code, and any later closure of the Source Code.

5.3. Redistribution of a Binary under this Section does not grant any right to obtain, modify, compile, rebuild, or otherwise use the corresponding Source Code except to the extent that such Source Code remains Covered Source or the recipient is otherwise separately authorized in writing.

